        <%= link_to "#fw-intro", :class => "btn btn-danger btn-lg btn-start", :id => 'btn-readon' do %>
        	<span class="action-text">Read on</span>&nbsp;
        	<i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-down fa-2x action-icon"></i>
        <% end %>      
      </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container" id="fw-intro">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-md-offset-1">
      <h3>What is fundwok?</h3>
    	<p>
    		fundwok is a marketplace for people to offer funds as little as $5. Funds can be offered to any number of people on a condition, or totally gratis, depending on the funder. fundwok is meant to facilitate resource sharing in a supportive and dynamic community where reliable resources can be effectively located and shared.
    	</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-md-offset-1 text-center">
      <i class="fa fa-comments about-icon"></i>
    </div>
  </div><!-- /.row -->
</div>


<div class="container">

  <hr class="featurette-divider">

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-5 col-sm-5 col-md-offset-1 text-center">
      <i class="fa fa-group about-icon"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4">
      <h3>
      	Who should be using fundwok?</h3>
      <p>
      	If creative projects are not the only thing you think should benefit from other people’s funds, fundwok is the place where sky's the limit. Got $20 for a cool coding lesson that got you started? Share it to a prospective programmer just like you used to be! Got $5 to treat someone a nice cup of coffee that you’d enjoy? Go make her day! 
      </p>
    </div>
  </div><!-- /.row -->

	<hr class="featurette-divider">

	<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-md-offset-1">
      <h3>How is fundwok<span style="vertical-align: super; font-size: 0.6em;">beta</span> different from the full launch version?</h3>
      	<p>
      		You won’t be giving out any of your pocket money. Instead, you’ll be giving out ours. (Woohoo!) All that you need is a facebook account to start spreading your love.
      	</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-md-offset-1 text-center">
      <i class="fa fa-wrench" style="font-size: 10em;"></i>
    </div>
  </div><!-- /.row -->
  <br />
  <br />
</div>

<div class="jumbotron" id="about-action">
  <div class="container" id="about-action-headline">
    <div class="row text-center">   
			<div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-center">
        <h2>Join the exclusive community</h2>
        <h3>Before others do.</h3>
        <% if current_user %>
          <%= link_to new_post_path, :class => "btn btn-fw btn-action", :id => "about-add-new-fund" do %>
            <span class="btn-action-content">+ Add New Fund</span>
          <% end %>
        <% else %>
          <%= link_to "#myModal", :data => {:toggle=>"modal"}, :class => "btn btn-danger btn-lg btn-start", :id => "about-join-fw-btn" do %>
            <div id="about-join-fw-content">
          	 <i class='fa fa-user'></i>&nbsp;
          	 <span class="about-join-fw-text">Join fundwok<span style="vertical-align: super; font-size: 0.5em;">beta</span></span>
            </div>
          <% end %>  
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
